Genetic Algorithms. 

Explanation: The paper focuses on the use of genetic algorithms to solve an optimization problem derived from the 3-Conjunctive Normal Form problem. The paper discusses the use of parallel genetic algorithms and hill-climbing techniques to improve the quality of solutions. The majority of the paper is dedicated to discussing the implementation and effectiveness of genetic algorithms in solving the problem. Therefore, the paper belongs to the sub-category of AI known as Genetic Algorithms.
